AttributeList.Text: ================================================================================ This module is used everywhere two alarms shall be generated from one object. The alarm can be True only when the input Enable Alarm is also True. The alarm can be True only when the input Disable Alarm is False. When the alarm is disable from HMI, a boolean output is available to inform the upper level and do action in the Alarm summary. When the conditions to generate the alarm is disappear, a boolean output is available to inform the upper level that the alarm can be reset. ================================================================================
